             sworn.</p>
               <p>I have known him nine or ten years; he is an honest, hard working man.</p>
               <p>
                  <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="177812090047"></xptr>
            
                  <persName id="t17781209-34-person438">
                  JOSHUA
                   SHINGLES
               <interp inst="t17781209-34-person438" type="surname" value="SHINGLES"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17781209-34-person438" type="given" value="JOSHUA"></interp>
