                  </persName>
             sworn.</p>
               <p>I have known Figges about eleven or twelve years; he is a very laborious, hard working man; he bears a good character.</p>
               <p>BOTH <rs id="t17781209-34-verdict218" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17781209-34-verdict218" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
               GUILTY
            </rs> 
                  <rs id="t17781209-34-punish219" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17781209-34-punish219" type="punishmentCategory" value="death"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17781209-34-defend420 t17781209-34-punish219"></join>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17781209-34-defend422 t17781209-34-punish219"></join>
               Death
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Tried by the First Middlesex Jury before Mr. Justice WILLES.</p>
